{"tid":18381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(突發) 懷仔終獲單程証居港權","createTime":"2016-12-02T09:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T10:13:25.000Z","uid":49457,"like":0,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"482f082dec29efc300f65a42cc500548c9049356","tid":18381,"uid":49457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:10:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/cat99/node1359360#6301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fcat99%2Fnode1359360%236301&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=f8baf486\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twgreatdaily.com/cat99/node1359360#6301</a><br />\n<br />\n(突發) 懷仔終獲單程証居港權 施麗珊「如果唔係中國政府，你班香港人會有得食? 唔好再攪住懷仔生活」<br />\n<br />\n一名聲稱遭父母遺棄的12歲內地男童肖友懷，被外婆周紹璇以他人身份成功申請單程証，匿藏9年無上學，昨由律師陪同下到入境處自首，獲港府酌情處理，成功給予外孫居留權。<br />\n<br />\n外婆昨涉嫌協助及教唆他人違反逗留條件被捕獲准保釋，男童則獲發「單程証」，懷仔可最快一個月後留港接受教育<br />\n<br />\n身形高大的肖友懷因無證件，一直未有入學，平日多數留在家，靠外婆教他讀書寫字<br />\n<br />\n「施麗珊」的圖片搜尋結果GreatDaily<br />\n<br />\n深圳地鐵上目睹專為大陸人搵香港福利的施麗珊與肖友懷（懷仔）及其外婆周紹璇一起，施不斷打電話，張羅懷仔回港事宜。施麗珊接受查找時承認相中人是她，但對網民指她正在協助懷仔回港，社工施麗珊斥拍攝「如果唔係中國政府，你班香港人會有得食? 唔好再攪住懷仔，去死啦你地」<br />\n<br />\n她又批評拍照者是無風起浪及侵犯別人隱私。她又稱懷仔目前處境很慘，懷仔以往外出亦曾被人拍照，令他不願外出<br />\n<br />\nGreatDaily<br />\n<br />\n施麗珊又指懷仔與外婆已不願再向傳媒透露近況，不接受訪問，故她也不方便再說更多，請讀者們「做好心」，「小朋友係無辜，唔好再講小朋友啲乜嘢，對佢心理影響好大&hellip;&hellip;佢唔係想話攞你香港啲乜嘢，點解唔放過佢呢？」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1404748c0748baa0bd0d6f91e60b858b59e10a7d","tid":18381,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:12:59.000Z","msg":"呢d政棍，專做埋d損害香港既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb1b5693a8299f866e954417b365f253699335ea","tid":18381,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:13:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1503efd4281f3bca7e0e1c4a406d79d2eccbe70","tid":18381,"uid":3007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"行街小心D<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3259bded86c38fbf3629797dc2a0114cb5baf407","tid":18381,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"今朝咪有人話係假新聞"},{"pid":"98126926c520d30212c88b2632375ca55f614fca","tid":18381,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:15:11.000Z","msg":"都痴撚線嘅"},{"pid":"d1092a182f87e1af7c62b7b81310776805cc0964","tid":18381,"uid":38122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"咁有骨氣唔好返黎啦<br />\n咁似牙joe"},{"pid":"febd7510c7b39b6ab464850d0ba108027ddacd56","tid":18381,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:15:19.000Z","msg":"又係香港人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8059807fae0763a01f1e22e4c9b4cea4bf859a0b","tid":18381,"uid":29014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:15:26.000Z","msg":"農場文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ....<br />\n希望巴打今晚面壁思過"},{"pid":"9170f2c084bb7531a93ca8657a5ea51d27930aa3","tid":18381,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T09:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n送畀樓主...唔洗多謝我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a07d9e641f5ee0a3a1db494c6955b59d89e2efe","tid":18381,"uid":6518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim